This paper deals with auditing and debugging deep learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on social applications suggests that it may also fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The mention of misclassifications and the need to alter decision boundaries suggests that it may also fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
